  "description": "A powerful, structured Node.js logger that turns messy stack traces into **clean, clickable VS Code links**. Designed specifically for Express developers who want to stay in the flow. Lognest Logger captures all the details you need, formats them beautifully, and saves them to MongoDB for easy retrieval and analysis. Say goodbye to scrolling through endless logs and hello to a more efficient debugging experience.",
